WEBVTT

00:12:28.352 --> 00:12:30.957
And for you, for all of us,

00:12:30.981 --> 00:12:34.091
it means finding a role to play
in our own communities.

00:12:34.777 --> 00:12:39.308
It means living your life as a reflection
of the world that you want to live in.

00:12:39.332 --> 00:12:42.749
It means trusting those
who know the problems best --

00:12:42.773 --> 00:12:44.301
the people who live them --

00:12:44.325 --> 00:12:45.482
with solutions.

00:12:46.919 --> 00:12:50.423
I know a third way is possible
because I have lived it.

00:12:50.845 --> 00:12:55.198
I live it right now

00:12:55.222 --> 00:12:56.794
in a neighborhood called Poletown

00:12:56.818 --> 00:12:59.186
in one of the most
maligned cities in the world.

00:12:59.640 --> 00:13:01.179
If we can do it in Detroit,